modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod adds blocks that aren't lootable in the vanilla game. Body Bags 7 types. Some have been cleared and others are still lootable.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds blocks that aren’t lootable in the vanilla game.

**Stage 1:**

* Body Bags 7 types
* Some have been cleared before the bodies were placed inside the bags others have been looted by people before your arrival. And others are still lootable.

**Still to do:**

Add more objects to the loot

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/stallionsden/stallionsmodlets/tree/main/Stallionsdens%20LootableObjects)**

If you appreciate Stallionsden’s work and you want to show support, use this [donate link](http://paypal.me/AnthonyCar78).
